 &UR; (To publish this excellent commentary, it must be purchased from
the New York Times Syndicate's sales representative DEBRA WEYDERT
at 732-390-4480, or fax her at 732-390-4697. Her e-mail address is
Debra/Weydert/CORPHQ/NYTIMES. If unable to reach Ms. Weydert,
please call 800-444-0267, or fax us at 816-822-1444.) &LR;  &QL;
</P>
