``k'' commentary news file.)  
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; COMMENTARY &LR;  &QC; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; YOUR MAJESTY, JORDAN NEEDS MORE DEMOCRACY, NOT ANOTHER
MONARCHY &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (ATTN: Commentary Editors) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Moved as BC-LEGACY-KING-HUSSEIN-ECONOMIST-NYTSF......700 words &QL; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; I.O.C. S.O.S.: GOLDEN RULES, NOT GOLDEN HANDSHAKES &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (ATTN: Commentary Editors) &QL;
</P>
<P>
