</P>
<P>
   In less than half a century, therefore, the Hashemites had lost
the Hejaz, Iraq and all of Palestine. &QL; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; (FIRST OPTIONAL TRIM _ 250 WORDS _ BEGINS HERE) &LR;  &QC; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Inevitably, the story of the Hashemites has become the story of
the Plucky Little King, who now lies dying in the Mayo Clinic.
</P>
<P>
