   58. IRWIN M. and JOAN K. JACOBS--$15 million to the UNIVERSITY
OF CALIFORNIA, SAN DIEGO.
</P>
<P>
   58. GEORGE DEAN JR. and SUSAN JOHNSON--$15 million to CONVERSE
COLLEGE (S.C.).
</P>
<P>
   58. BERNARD OSHER--$15 million, inlcuding $10 million to the
UNIVERSITY OF CALIFORNIA AT SAN FRANCISCO.
</P>
<P>
   58. GERALD ``RED'' RATNER--$15 million to the UNIVERSITY OF
CHICAGO.
</P>
<P>
   58. HENRY R. SILVERMAN--$15 million to the UNIVERSITY OF
PENNSYLVANIA Law School.
</P>
<P>
   58. ROBERT H. SMITH--$15 million to the UNIVERSITY OF MARYLAND
AT COLLEGE PARK business school.
</P>
<P>
