<DOCNO> NYT19990204.0167 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-02-04 13:12 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1735 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-GARDEN-COLUMN-BOS &LR;      02-04 1353
