<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-02-04 13:31 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1767 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FILM-SUNDANCE-HNS &LR;      02-04 0958
