Florida when it capsized near Elliott Key. Fourteen people drowned.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  On Oct. 3, 1998 -- 462 Haitians were intercepted 15 miles west
of Orange Cay, Bahamas on their way from Haiti to South Florida.
