<P>
   TRAVEL-TEXAS-CORPUS-HNS (Corpus Christi, Texas) _ Easily the
largest city along the lower Texas coast, Corpus Christi maintains
a low-key ambience. Its heart is at the waterfront, where
restaurants tempt with the mouth-watering catch of the day and
old-style seafood shops market a bounty of riches. By Harry
Shattuck.
