<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-02-04 17:44 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2120 &Cx1f; tab-z
r l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-TEMPLETON-INNOVATORS-     02-04 0997
