<P>
   NBA PREVIEW
</P>
<P>
   BKN-NBA -PREVIEW _ A 50-game season with a crowded schedule.
Free agents moving everywhere. Short training camps. It's an
unpredictable NBA season that begins Friday, though one thing
appears certain _ the Bulls won't repeat. (Bunn, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   WITH
</P>
<P>
   BKN-NBA-BRIEFS _ Who's in and out of shape, who's most likely to
succeed, etc. (Bunn, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
