<P>
   BKN-NBA-WEST _ Western Conference caps (Denberg, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   BKN-HAWKS _ Hawks preview. Roster changes, ticket sales,
promotions. (Denberg, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   NBA - Fifty games to the finish line. We take a look at the
elements that will help some teams and hurt others in this
abbreviated season. Brutal schedule. Injuries. Who's in shape?
Who's not? (D'Angelo, Palm Beach Post)
</P>
<P>
   HEAT-MOURNING - Pat Riley says it's time for Alonzo Mourning to
step up and carry this team to a championship. But can he or did
the Heat spend $100 million on a brooding, temperamental guy who
can't come through in the clutch? (Rosenberg, Palm Beach Post)
</P>
<P>
   NBA-STODA - Columnist Greg Stoda's take on the return of the
NBA. (Stoda, Palm Beach Post)
</P>
<P>
   MOTORSPORTS
</P>
<P>
   RAC-DAYTONA-ADVANCE _ DAYTONA BEACH, Fla. _ Advance Saturday's
opening of Speedweek with pole qualifying for Daytona 500.
