   Fifth Avenue and 82nd Street
</P>
<P>
   Through April 25
</P>
<P>
   `FRENCH MASTER DRAWINGS FROM THE 16TH THROUGH 18TH CENTURIES'
</P>
<P>
   Wildenstein &AMP; Co.
</P>
<P>
   19 E. 64th St.
</P>
<P>
   Through May 1
</P>
<P>
   `FIGURE AND FANTASY IN FRENCH PAINTING, 1650-1800'
</P>
<P>
   Berry-Hill Gallery
</P>
<P>
   11 E. 70th Street
</P>
<P>
   Through March. 6
</P>
<P>
   `DROUAIS' PORTRAIT OF MADAME DE POMPADOUR FROM THE NATIONAL
GALLERY, LONDON'
</P>
<P>
   The Frick Collection
</P>
<P>
   1 E. 70th St.
</P>
<P>
   Through April 25
</P>
</TEXT>
