   In keeping with ``the current trend of lounge music and tiki
decor'' and a proposed Museum of Velvet Painting in Seattle, the
Huntington Beach Art Center's show of ``The Velvet Paintings of
Edgar Leeteg'' opens F &LR; eb. &LR;   &LR; 7 &LR; .
